Chuck Berry has either directly or indirectly influenced nearly every artist in rock music, including such superstars as John Lennon, Paul McCartney, Mick Jagger, Keith Richards, Brian Wilson and Bruce Springsteen, to name a few. His simple riffs have been copied by millions and his songs have been covered too many times to be remembered. "Maybellene", "Johnny B. Goode", "Carol", "Sweet Little Sixteen", "Around & Around" and all the other original gems included here are simple two-and-a-half-minute songs that convey all the sheer power and emotion of Rock 'n' Roll. Budget compilation of some of his greatest hits.
